short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quick and Easy Access to your saved browser tabs!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This browser extension allows you to save and label all your current browser tabs and get back to them later. Incase you are sharing a computer or need to shutdown your computer but do not want to lose your tabs, this browser extension is the best way to solve this problem.
